# 如何设计和实现
# 以sort函数为例，展示过程

1 从最简单情况开始，如排序整数序列，而后扩展到其他类型
2 排序意味着什么？
Sorting means rearranging a bunch of numbers.

# 数据类型的转换 input data type——>output type
This restatement implies a natural data definition for the inputs and outputs of the function and thus its signature.

# 主函数的签名，主要包括输入和输出的数据类型
Given that we have a definition for List-of-numbers, the first step is easy:
----------------------------------------
; List-of-numbers -> List-of-numbers 
; produces a sorted version of alon
(define (sort> alon)
  alon)
----------------------------------------

